videos.description: Desi Rodriguez ignites fast break with a full court pass to Myles Powell for a Pirates bucket.
videos.headline: Seton Hall's Rodriguez with a  full court pass to Powell for layup

videos.description: Keenan Evans races the distance a scores a right-handed layup for the Red Raiders.
videos.headline: Texas Tech's Evans goes coast-to-coast for layup

videos.description: Eron Gordon makes spot up 3-pointer off the pass from Myles Powell for the Pirates.
videos.headline: Gordon swishes a 3-pointer for Seton Hall

videos.description: Micheal Nzei right-handed layup gives the Pirates a 29-27 lead in the first half.
videos.headline: Carrington feeds Nzei on bucket

videos.description: Keenan Evans dunk off the feed from Zhaire Smith gives the Red Raiders the lead 39-37 in the first half.
videos.headline: Texas Tech's Evans slams fast break dunk for the lead

videos.description: Ismael Sanogo banks in the shot off the feed from Myles Powell for the Pirates.
videos.headline: Sanogo banks it in for Seton Hall

videos.description: Keenan Evans hits a 3-pointer off the screen from Zach Smith to pull the Red Raiders within three 65-62 in the second half.
videos.headline: Evans swishes a 3-pointer for Texas Tech

videos.description: Myles Powell hits a 3-pointer off the pass from Desi Rodriguez to extend the Pirates' lead in the second half.
videos.headline: Seton Hall's Powell with a 3-pointer to extend lead

videos.description: Khadeen Carrington up-and-under basket extends the lead for the Pirates to 75-65 in the second half.
videos.headline: Carrington's up-and-under bucket extends the lead for Seton Hall

videos.description: Keenan Evans scores layup with the Eurostep to draw the Red Raiders closer.
videos.headline: Evans with the Eurostep for layup
